  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[Security] Play this card without paying the cost.\n[Start
    of Your Main Phase] By trashing 1 card with the [Machine]/[Cyborg]/[SoC]\_trait
    in your hand, gain 1 memory.\n[Main] \uFF1CMind Link\uFF1E (Place this Tamer
    as that Digimon's bottom digivolution card if there are no Tamer cards in its
    digivolution cards) with 1 of your Digimon with the [Machine]/[Cyborg]/[SoC]\_trait."
  InheritedEffectDiscription_JPN: 
  InheritedEffectDiscription_ENG: "[All Turns] While this Digimon has the [Machine]/[Cyborg]/[SoC]\_trait,
    it gains \uFF1CJamming\uFF1Eand \uFF1CBlocker\uFF1E \n[End of All Turns] You
    may play 1 [Marvin Jackson] from this Digimon's digivolution cards without paying
    the cost."
